## Always-Loaded Context

These two files are always small and always relevant. Read them at session start:

- [`systems/tracker/ACTIVE.md`](../../systems/tracker/ACTIVE.md) — current project state, active goals, last 3 actions
- [`systems/learnings/INSIGHTS.md`](../../systems/learnings/INSIGHTS.md) — top working insights about this project and how to work well in it

