## Trigger Map

| User says | Agent does |
|-----------|------------|
| `"compile log"` / `"what have I done"` | Read tracker raw logs since last compile → generate weekly summary |
| `"compile learnings"` / `"learning review"` | Read learnings raw logs + research → generate digest, ask about adoptions |
| `"search for [topic]"` / `"what's new in [topic]"` | Web search → save to `systems/learnings/research/` → summarise findings |
| `"init framework"` / `"bootstrap project"` | Run init-framework skill |
| `"upgrade framework"` / `"audit framework"` | Run upgrade-framework skill |
| `"what's next"` / `"project status"` | Read `ACTIVE.md` → summarise state + suggest next action |
| Building any UI | Read `systems/design/visual-system.md` and `systems/design/tokens.md` first |
| Adding a dependency | Check `systems/architecture/dependencies.md` before deciding |
| Anything security-related | Read `systems/security/_INDEX.md` first |

